name: FNF Tricky Test (StefanN)
description:
FNF Tricky Test - All his phases!

In this game you can test all Tricky's phases:

  • Test Tricky Phase 0
  • Test Tricky Phase 0.5
  • Test Tricky Phase 1
  • Test Tricky Phase 2
  • Test Tricky Phase 3
  • Test Tricky Phase 4
  • Test Tricky Phase 5

In total, I added 7 different phases including some fan-made ones. Like all of my Fnf test mods online, here you will have animations, special moves, vocals, and instrumentals. Tricky the clown test game is my biggest Friday Night Funkin test game until now.

Of course, this is a Fnf online test game, so you can play it from any device - PC, laptop, tablet, smartphone, or even watch if you have one smart enough.

If you want, we can talk on Discord: https://discord.gg/jA43fs5NhE

Feel free to make videos on Youtube, images, anything with the game. If you could credit me for those that will be great! :)
